        "Rules": {
          "HelpTitle": "Combat Duel Rules",
          "HelpHtml": "<div style=\"font-family:'Signika',sans-serif; line-height:1.5; color:#1a1a1a; padding:15px; background:url('ui/parchment.jpg'); border:2px solid #540000;\"><h2 style=\"border-bottom:2px solid #700; color:#700; text-align:center; font-family:'Modesto Condensed', serif;\">COMBAT DUEL</h2><p><b>Goal:</b> inflict Wounds equal to the opponent's death threshold. It is 4 by default; <i>Diehard</i> raises it and <i>Doomed</i> lowers it.</p><p><b>Round:</b> each duelist secretly sets 3 action slots and both sides resolve them simultaneously.</p><h3 style=\"color:#900;\">1. ACTIONS</h3><ul><li><b>Attack:</b> selected weapon vs AC. Success deals 1 Wound, critical success deals 2 Wounds.</li><li><b>Defense:</b> total defense. Hostile checks against the duelist are rolled with disadvantage: 2d20 and keep the lower result.</li><li><b>Maneuver:</b> Athletics vs Fortitude, Acrobatics vs Reflex, Intimidation vs Will, Deception vs Perception. Success gives the target -2 AC next round, critical success also removes 1 action.</li></ul><h3 style=\"color:#900;\">2. ACTION INTERACTION</h3><ul><li><b>Attack vs Defense:</b> the attacker rolls with disadvantage.</li><li><b>Maneuver vs Attack:</b> the maneuvering duelist takes -2 to the roll.</li><li><b>Maneuver vs Defense:</b> the defense is broken and the defender's DC is reduced by 2.</li></ul><h3 style=\"color:#900;\">3. MAP</h3><p>Multiple attack penalty is tracked separately for Attack and for each Maneuver type: 0 / -4 / -8.</p></div>",
          "SidebarHtml": "<div style=\"margin-bottom:10px; line-height: 1.3;\">\n  <b>Goal:</b> Inflict Wounds equal to the opponent's death threshold. It is 4 by default; <i>Diehard</i> raises it and <i>Doomed</i> lowers it.<br>\n  <b>Actions:</b> 3 slots per round.<br>\n  <hr style=\"border-color:#4a0404; margin: 8px 0;\">\n  <b>🗡️ Attack:</b> selected weapon vs AC.<br>\n  • <i style=\"color:#2ecc71\">Success:</i> 1 Wound | <i style=\"color:#2ecc71\">Crit:</i> 2 Wounds<br>\n  <b>🛡️ Defense:</b> total defense.<br>\n  <b>🤹 Maneuver:</b> Athletics vs Fortitude, Acrobatics vs Reflex, Intimidation vs Will, Deception vs Perception.<br>\n  • <i style=\"color:#2ecc71\">Success:</i> target -2 AC | <i style=\"color:#2ecc71\">Crit:</i> -2 AC and -1 action<br>\n  <hr style=\"border-color:#4a0404; margin: 8px 0;\">\n  <b>Action interaction:</b><br>\n  • <i>Attack vs Defense:</i> attacker rolls with Misfortune.<br>\n  • <i>Maneuver vs Attack:</i> maneuvering duelist takes <b>-2</b>.<br>\n  • <i>Maneuver vs Defense:</i> defense is broken. Defender's DC is reduced by <b>-2</b>.<br>\n  <hr style=\"border-color:#4a0404; margin: 8px 0;\">\n  <b>MAP:</b> tracked <b>separately</b> for Attack and each Maneuver type: 0 / -4 / -8. Defense has no penalty.\n</div>"
        },
